{
  "stem": "21786.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Like Genghis Khan soldiers in these stripe uniforms, the caps down, and we were-- our hair was cut short and we had here a cross, done with a razor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So it looked-- we looked terrific.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he had the speech to us that we are here to work to death, that they will work us to death.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we will work and work and work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But should we just look at one of these German women, immediate death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I mean, he spoke for about five minutes, 10 minutes, and we heard that at least 10 times.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then he made a crucial mistake.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He turned towards the six German women and gave them a pep talk, forgetting that they are free German citizens.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So that when he left, so they all were trying to get something out of us, for they realized we speak German.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the head of the laundry, her name was Ruhl-- like in the [INAUDIBLE]-- R-U-H-L.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was telling me-- we are putting sheets through [INAUDIBLE] rollers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She spoke to me, I mean, what-- what are you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why did we come there [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I finally said, madam, I cannot talk to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She says, for you to be shot I would have to report you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, who says that you will not report me?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She says, I say so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For my two sons who are taken prisoners by the Americans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if this is what the Americans are doing to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I said, madam, I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I can tell you, every morning, kneel down and pray to your God that they are with the Americans, that they are not with your people.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
